1. *Promeni* pažnju koju poklanjaš drugima. (Change the attention you give to others.)

2. Ona je *promenila* svoje mišljenje. (She changed her mind.)

3. *Promenila* je stav prema njemu. (She changed her attitude towards him.)

4. On je *promenio* svoje navike. (He changed his habits.)

5. *Promeni* način na koji postupaš. (Change the way you act.)

6. Oni su *promenili* svoje živote. (They changed their lives.)